erests, but having\nthe bettering of conditions of the community in\nwhich they live at heart, and can always be found\nback of any movement that will redound to the bet\nterment of Mt. Sterling and Montgomery county.\nNot only do they handle the best of merchandise\nand give satisfactory service, but they save their l1\ncustomers MANY DOLLARS and it is a generally I\nrecognized fact that a housekeeper can save money w\nby trading with them. If you have never given them A\na trial they invite your patronage, assuring you they M\nwill make it worth your while.\nThe members of this large and enterprising fi\nbusiness are all optimistists of the first water and M\nf irmly believe we are entering upon an era of unpre- I\ncedented prosperity and are confident that the so- y\ncalled business depression following the re-adjust- A\nment period, is at an end and that more profitable U\nand larger business will be enjoyed by our mer- R\nchants, and the business -world generally, from now\non than we have ever known in our history.\nSpring Shirts of class nnd character. Solid colors, stripos anil\nchecks. Detachable collars and attached collars. Manv imported\nmaterials. All tailored in some of America's moit famous short shops\nTRUTH-CASH\nONE PRICE\n:?r:3?2sn353sr33\nmm co.\n;sr5ss3CPssr\"\nLet ME Do YOUR SSSQE IEPAlilEli\nNO PROFITEERING PRICES\nNothing but best grades of\nleather used.\nWork guaranteed to give sat\nisfaction. COURTEOUS TREATMENT\n\"The Shop With a Smile\"\nW. M. Riessinger\nPrompt Service Opposite Courthouse\n32\nFor Health and Strength\nThere is nothing so pure and good for your\nstomach's sake than a bottle of Lime or Orange\nCrush Soda \"Water. Manufactured by the Mt. Ster\nling Bottling \"Works. No home complete \"without a\ncase.\nGIVE US A TRIAL ORDER\nMT. STERLING B0TTL1H6 WORKS\nCLAUDE P. STEPHENS, Proprietor\nAND MAKER OP GOOD CRACKER JACK\nEast Locust Street\nIsaescKrKSfBSwKiCE:\nsatsrKirEsgrssscs'ilEaas:\nPhono 265\n3ASril'2r\naKmUmWTa\n,---frr 